                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>After dark, Lavinia loses all reason and becomes overtaken by the curse. She loses the ability to speak and attacks the PCs on sight. While haunted by the night, Lavinia is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Quickened], and can use the extra action to make a ghostly hand Strike.</p>"
